:Server: as server << application >>
:Player: as player << Human >>
:Bot: as bot << bot >>
(Start game) as (start)
(Initialize Game) as (init)
(Game starts) as (gameStart)

server --> (start)
server --> (init)
(init) ..> player : signals
(init) ..> bot : signals
player --> (init)
bot --> (init)
(init) --> (gameStart)

note right of (init)
